---
title: Gmail 5-Tier Filter 設定
description: clasp 安裝 → 登入 → 建專案 → 推送 → 引導執行
links:
  - setup-main: 返回主流程
  - setup-status: 調整配置
---
flowchart TD
    Start([setupGmailFilters]) --> HasPrev{session 有 scriptId?}
    HasPrev -->|Yes| KeepQ[保持不變？]
    KeepQ -->|Yes| ReturnPrev([返回現有設定])
    KeepQ -->|No/ESC| Continue

    HasPrev -->|No| Continue[Step 1: 檢查 clasp]
    Continue --> ClaspCheck{clasp 已安裝?}
    ClaspCheck -->|No| InstallQ[安裝 clasp？]
    InstallQ -->|Yes| NpmInstall[npm install -g @google/clasp]
    InstallQ -->|No| Manual([顯示手動步驟])
    NpmInstall -->|失敗| Manual
    NpmInstall -->|成功| LoginCheck

    ClaspCheck -->|Yes| LoginCheck{Step 2: clasp 已登入?}
    LoginCheck -->|No| Login[clasp login → 開啟瀏覽器]
    Login -->|失敗| Manual
    Login -->|成功| Prepare
    LoginCheck -->|Yes| Prepare

    Prepare[Step 3: 準備暫存目錄] --> CopyFiles[複製 .gs + appsscript.json]
    CopyFiles --> AutoDetect{session 有 scriptId?}

    AutoDetect -->|Yes| Reuse["Step 4: 複用現有專案
    寫入 .clasp.json"]
    AutoDetect -->|No| Create[Step 4: clasp create]

    Create --> CreateResult{成功?}
    CreateResult -->|API 未啟用| OpenAPI["自動開啟設定頁面
    https://script.google.com/home/usersettings"]
    OpenAPI --> WaitUser[等用戶開啟 API]
    WaitUser --> RetryCreate[重試 clasp create]
    RetryCreate --> CreateResult
    CreateResult -->|成功| Push
    CreateResult -->|失敗 ×3| Manual

    Reuse --> Push

    Push["Step 5: clasp push --force
    (async spinner)"] --> PushResult{成功?}
    PushResult -->|失敗| Manual
    PushResult -->|成功| Done

    Done[Step 6: 部署完成] --> OpenEditor["自動開啟 Apps Script 編輯器"]
    OpenEditor --> Guide["引導用戶：
    1. 選函式 setupAndApply
    2. 點擊 ▶ 執行
    3. 授權 Gmail API
    ─────────────
    效果：
    Tier 0 GitHub/CI → github/noise 標籤
    Tier 1 SaaS bot → auto/skip 標籤
    Tier 2 公告/收據 → auto/info 標籤
    Tier 3 行事曆 → auto/meeting 標籤
    Tier 4 HR/財務/緊急 → ⭐ STARRED + action/required"]
    Guide --> Return(["返回 { scriptId, scriptUrl }"])
